<div><div id='zzq7jg2531891jkRiverDetailGadget2' class='CRiverDetailGadget-detail CRiverDetailGadget'><div class='controls'><h1>Lovell - Pine Hill Road and Route 25</h1>
<div><div id='zzq7jg2531891jkArticleGadget26Container' class='CArticleGadget-view CArticleGadget'><div id='zzq7jg2531891jkArticleGadget26-1' class='contents'></div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
